      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. The engine has suffered a major internal failure and will likely require a full rebuild or replacement to run again. Additionally, the transmission is unresponsive, and there is significant frame rust and body damage that needs professional attention. This would be an ideal purchase for someone looking for a dedicated parts car or an extensive long-term restoration project. Please expect to tow this vehicle from its current location.",
